\n護士清算左未<br />\n日日角色扮演<br />\n<br />\n有無八ha secre t 死仆街<br />\n訓左無睇吖<br />\n<br />\n615 又開關啦<br />\n又利用醫護喇<br />\n<br />\n正垃圾 醫護罷工<br />\n捍衛自己專業 <br />\n捍衛香港安全<br />\n<br />\n你班死仆街<br />\n自己驚死 唔敢罷工<br />\n開埋工會 比你地加油聚人頭<br />\n喂到入口 死都唔出聲<br />\n唔敢出聲咪airdrop文宣囉<br />\n<br />\n家陣叫你去死哶<br />\n罷工要坐監咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成年人都唔夠學生識衡量價值<br />\n<br />\n垃圾連仔ban9我喇<br />\n我係要周圍痴旮旯<br />\n<br />\n死仆街五毛唔搞日日ban9我<br />\n你最威喇仆街連仔<br />\n連仔死仆街</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"a48bfe102a05bf22f8a6d6b3ef47f57c5be2cc82","tid":2059953,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T16:29:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01aed90f6c4b777e58f0d22637e30ed11c504a4","tid":2059953,"uid":198071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T22:32:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e71b2bbaea94a29057a9c3b64acd6e36536bf371","tid":2059953,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T05:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b981b5b8f73052907e49e597fd936081be2b1d","tid":2059953,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af25bbb8feef84de8bc535ee12ef8d175812abaf","tid":2059953,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68c9fe656e0c2627960247d8691410fac630d8b1","tid":2059953,"uid":127466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T10:04:51.000Z","msg":"副局腸同埋教聯會班人簡東話都講唔正又咪做教育 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T10:39:49.000Z","msg":"最垃圾先可以做到高位"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T05:48:03.